---
import LayoutPage from "../../layouts/LayoutPage.astro";
import { getLangFromUrl } from "../../i18n/utils";
import { getHomePath } from "../../i18n/paths";

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const homeHref = getHomePath(lang);

const lastUpdated = "April 12, 2025";
---

<LayoutPage
  title="Terms & Conditions | sonmyd — Miguel Zuluaga"
  description="Terms and conditions for the Artificial Intelligence mentorship service by Miguel Zuluaga (sonmyd)."
>
  <div class="page-wrap">
    <div class="u-container content">
      <a href={homeHref} class="back-link">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M17 10a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75H5.612l4.158 3.96a.75.75 0 1 1-1.04 1.08l-5.5-5.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.08l5.5-5.25a.75.75 0 1 1 1.04 1.08L5.612 9.25H16.25A.75.75 0 0 1 17 10Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        {lang === "en" ? "Back to home" : "Volver al inicio"}
      </a>

      <h1 class="u-heading page-title">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="meta u-text">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose u-text">
        <p>
          These Terms and Conditions govern the contracting and use of AI mentorship services offered by
          <strong>Miguel Zuluaga</strong> under the brand <strong>sonmyd</strong>
          (hereinafter, "the Provider"). By booking or contracting any service, the user (hereinafter,
          "the Client") fully accepts these terms.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Service description</h2>
        <p>
          sonmyd offers 1-on-1 Artificial Intelligence classes, fully online via video call
          (Google Meet or Zoom). The available services are:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Free diagnosis session:</strong> an initial 30-minute session, at no cost, to
            assess the Client's level and define the most suitable plan.</li>
          <li><strong>Individual Session:</strong> 60-minute session, with support material and class recording included.</li>
          <li><strong>Intensive Package:</strong> 10 hours of classes distributed across multiple sessions, with curated
            materials, recordings of all classes, continuous follow-up and a real portfolio project.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Booking and confirmation</h2>
        <p>
          Booking any service is done through the channels enabled on the website (contact form
          or WhatsApp). The service is considered booked only once the Provider confirms
          availability and, when applicable, payment is received.
        </p>
        <p>
          The free diagnosis session is introductory in nature and implies no obligation to contract
          any subsequent plan.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Fees and payments</h2>
        <p>
          Current rates are published at <a href="https://sonmyd.co">sonmyd.co</a> and may be
          updated at any time. The applicable price is the one in effect at the time of booking confirmation.
        </p>
        <p>
          Payment is arranged directly with the Provider through available methods (bank transfer,
          PayPal or others agreed upon). The Intensive Package may require full or partial advance payment
          as agreed.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Cancellations and refunds</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Cancellation with more than 24 hours notice:</strong> the Client may reschedule the session
            at no cost.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Cancellation with less than 24 hours:</strong> the session will be considered consumed, unless
            a force majeure event is duly communicated.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Refunds for the Intensive Package:</strong> if the Client withdraws before completing half
            the sessions, a proportional refund of unused sessions will be provided, minus a 10%
            administrative fee. No refunds apply once half the package is completed.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Cancellation by the Provider:</strong> if the Provider cancels a confirmed session
            without rescheduling within a reasonable timeframe, a full refund of the paid amount for that session
            will be processed.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Use of materials</h2>
        <p>
          Materials, presentations, exercises and resources shared during classes are for the Client's
          exclusive personal use for learning. Reproduction, distribution, sale or publication without
          express written authorization from the Provider is prohibited.
        </p>
        <p>
          Class recordings are for the Client's personal use. They may not be shared, published or
          used for commercial purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Client conduct</h2>
        <p>
          The Client agrees to maintain respectful communication during all sessions. The Provider
          reserves the right to terminate the service relationship without refund in case of
          disrespectful conduct or misuse of the service.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>
          The Provider does not guarantee specific results (employment, income, certifications) as a direct
          consequence of the classes. Results depend on the effort, dedication and particular context of each
          Client. The service consists of personalized education and guidance in AI.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Modification of terms</h2>
        <p>
          The Provider may update these Terms and Conditions at any time. Changes will be published
          on this page with the update date. Continued use of the service after publication of
          changes implies acceptance of the new terms.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Applicable law and jurisdiction</h2>
        <p>
          These terms are governed by the laws of the Republic of Colombia. Any dispute that cannot
          be resolved amicably will be submitted to the jurisdiction of the competent courts of the city
          of Medellín, Colombia.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For any inquiries related to these terms, you can contact us via
          <a href="https://wa.me/573106041144" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LayoutPage>

<style>
  .page-wrap {
    padding: 9rem 0 8rem;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4em;
    color: rgba(240, 240, 250, 0.5);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;

    svg { width: 1em; height: 1em; }
    &:hover { color: rgba(240, 240, 250, 0.9); }
  }

  .content { max-width: 48rem; }

  .page-title {
    --fs: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;

    @media (--mq-phone) { --fs: 2.2rem; }
  }

  .meta {
    --fs: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-alt);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .prose {
    --fs: var(--font-size-sm);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(240, 240, 250, 0.8);

    p { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

    h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-roboto-slab);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgb(var(--rgb-text));
      margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(50, 170, 255, 0.15);
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;

      li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.7; }
    }

    strong { color: rgb(var(--rgb-text)); font-weight: 600; }

    a {
      color: rgb(var(--rgb-brand-2));
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-decoration-color: rgba(50, 170, 255, 0.4);
      transition: text-decoration-color 0.2s;

      &:hover { text-decoration-color: rgba(50, 170, 255, 1); }
    }
  }
</style>
